                                      rdfs:comment "Describes transport modality of the transport service" ;
                                      rdfs:label "Used transport modality" .


###  https://ontology.tno.nl/logistics/federated/DigitalTwin#goodsTypeCode
DigitalTwin:goodsTypeCode rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


